description:
Her Symphogear is Third Relic - Gungnir (ガングニール), which originally belonged to Kanade. However since it is only a fragment, she possesses less armor compared to the original and has no weapons or Arms Gear. She compensates for this by specialising in powerful martial arts, using short bursts of energy and pistons to power her punches or launch herself great distances.
Source: Wiki
name: Tachibana Hibiki
